typinglb.text: You must have a goal because it's just as difficult to reach a destination you don't have, as it is to come back from a place you've never been.
Be open to your dreams, people. Embrace that distant shore. Because our mortal journey is over all too soon.
And when the car broke down, they started walking. But where were they going without ever knowing the way?
I received special training via a secret organization working under the direct control of the President. I was to assume the responsibility of protecting the new President's family.
